, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.35,0.59", "scale": 1.5, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們一路嘗試透過食用魔物來填飽肚子。", "x": 300.0, "y": 550.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.65,0.47", "scale": 1.5, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "雖然這樣很艱苦，但是我們也獲得了新的夥伴，解決了一路上遇到的各種問題，也對這座迷宮有了全新的認識。", "x": 300.0, "y": 550.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但是在我們慢慢深入，以為一切順利時，好像又陷入了新的困境……", "x": 300.0, "y": 550.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.25, "fillto": 0.5, "fadetime": 1.5, "a": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.25, "fillto": 0.5, "fadetime": 1.5, "a": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "a