, "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種堅硬的外殼已經保護到了牠最柔弱的腹部，通常會有大量神經的脖頸也覆蓋了毫無縫隙的外殼。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "單憑我們的武器可能很難一下子把牠殺死。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾，用你的魔法！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用小一點的魔法，不要破壞這裡的生態環境！", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在也放不出更大的魔法了！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#10$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1430_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，也就是走路菇的水準。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然是新型的魔物！瑪露希爾你沒事吧？被牠攻擊的感覺如何？"